{
  "texts": [
    "As such, future automation studies may need to target this stage.",
    "Finally, in automating the RoB, the two related works focused on RCTs; thus, such automation needs to be extended to non-RCTs.",
    "Another novel area of exploration could be exploring how the human-in-the-loop strategy, active learning, might help in RoB classification.",
    "Also, one significant observation to be realised across all the related studies is that all focused on only English datasets except for Schmidt et al. (2020); thus, current SR automation studies are skewed towards English datasets.",
    "This opens a novel field of exploring which concepts will best automate either partially or fully non-English SRs."
  ]
}